User
    ident Text
    password Text Maybe
    familyName Text
    givenName Text

    UniqueUser ident
    deriving Show Eq Typeable

Issue
    subject Text
    description Textarea Maybe

    limitdate Day Maybe
    limittime TimeOfDay Maybe

    opener UserId
    created UTCTime default=now()
    updated UTCTime default=now()

    deriving Show Eq

Channel
    type     Logic
    issue    IssueId

    deriving Show Eq

Ticket
    channel  ChannelId
    domain   UserId
    codomain UserId
    assign   UserId
    status   Status

    created UTCTime default=now()
    updated UTCTime default=now()

    deriving Show Eq

Comment
    ticket  TicketId
    comment Textarea
    speaker UserId

    created UTCTime default=now()
    updated UTCTime default=now()

    deriving Show Eq

 -- By default this file is used in Model.hs (which is imported by Foundation.hs)
